snippet.title: Barnaba feat Diamond Platnumz - Salama (Official Lyric Audio)
snippet.description:
This heartfelt Collaboration between Barnaba and Diamond Platnumz tells the emotional story of a man reaching out to his ex-lover, asking how she’s doing now that she’s moved on. The lyrics reveal a mix of reflection and subtle confrontation, as he acknowledges that she seems to be thriving in a new relationship filled with peace, joy, and genuine love—something they lacked in the past. The song carries an undertone of regret and unresolved emotions, while also calling out the ex for once treating him as if he wasn’t good enough. Now, having found someone who truly values him, he indirectly questions her past judgments. It’s a soulful, melodic piece that explores themes of growth, healing, and the bittersweet nature of moving on. This song marks Barnaba’s Celebrations of 16 years in his role as a performing artist while still having a lot to achieve he remains focused to achieve a lot and climb heights of excellency on his music journey, while you listen to this track be inspired of greatness and enjoy the best sounds from the best.
